<font size="16sp">
The debate competition meant to test your skills in debate. 
Get ready for some heated debate on some most trending topics around the world. 
Do your homework because you won't get a second chance if you miss a point. 
<br>
<br>
<b>Rules and Regulations</b>
<br>
<br>
Debate on topics assigned.
<br>
Number of teams per college 1 max.
<br>
Member per team 2 max.
<br>
Event Fees 200/- per team.
<br>
Each participate would speak <i>for the motion</i>. 
<br>
Time limit of speech is up to 3-4 minutes.
<br>
<i>Rebuttal round</i> will be of 5 minutes.
